---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-navy text-white py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-40 gradient-radial"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/15 bg-navy-light/70 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-10 shadow-2xl">
        <p class="text-yellow font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mt-2 text-yellow">HumTech Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white text-sm sm:text-base">
          Last updated: January 20, 2026
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-off-white leading-relaxed">
          HumTech ("HumTech", "we", "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data.
          This policy explains how we handle personal data when you visit our website and outlines your rights under UK GDPR.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-navy py-10 lg:py-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 space-y-6">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Important Information</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white leading-relaxed">
          This policy covers data collection via our website, contact forms, and service enquiries. Our website targets
          business users (SMEs) and does not collect children's data. Please read this policy alongside any service-specific notices.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Controller</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white leading-relaxed">
          HumTech (United Kingdom) is the controller of website visitor data. For Data Subject Access Requests or rights queries, email
          <a href="mailto:hello@humtech.ai" class="text-blue-light hover:text-yellow underline underline-offset-4 ml-1">hello@humtech.ai</a>.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white leading-relaxed">
          Our site links to third-party services including Google Analytics and Meta Pixel. We do not control these third-party
          services and recommend reviewing their privacy policies.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Data We Collect</h2>
        <div class="mt-5 overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full min-w-[520px] border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/20">
                <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 text-yellow">Category</th>
                <th class="text-left py-3 text-yellow">Examples</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-off-white">
              <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Identity</td>
                <td class="py-3">Name, job title, company</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Contact</td>
                <td class="py-3">Email, phone, business address</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Technical</td>
                <td class="py-3">IP address, browser type, device</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Usage</td>
                <td class="py-3">Pages visited, time spent, referral source</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Marketing</td>
                <td class="py-3">Newsletter preferences, enquiry history</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white leading-relaxed">
          We also use aggregated, anonymous statistics for website performance analysis.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">How We Collect Data</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-off-white">
          <li><strong>Direct:</strong> Contact forms, service enquiries, demo requests.</li>
          <li><strong>Automated:</strong> Cookies, server logs, Google Analytics, Meta Pixel.</li>
          <li><strong>Third parties:</strong> Google (analytics), Meta (ads).</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <div class="mt-5 overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full min-w-[560px] border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/20">
                <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 text-yellow">Purpose</th>
                <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 text-yellow">Legal Basis</th>
                <th class="text-left py-3 text-yellow">Example</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-off-white">
              <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Service delivery</td>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4">Contract</td>
                <td class="py-3">Processing AI implementation enquiries</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Site functionality</td>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4">Legitimate interest</td>
                <td class="py-3">Analytics for UX improvements</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Marketing</td>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4">Consent</td>
                <td class="py-3">Email newsletters (opt-out anytime)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Security</td>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4">Legal obligation</td>
                <td class="py-3">Fraud prevention and spam filtering</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Marketing</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-off-white">
          <li>We may send communications if you have enquired about AI services.</li>
          <li>We do not share your details for third-party marketing without explicit opt-in.</li>
          <li>Opt out by clicking "Unsubscribe" or emailing <a href="mailto:hello@humtech.ai" class="text-blue-light hover:text-yellow underline underline-offset-4">hello@humtech.ai</a>.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Cookies</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-off-white">
          <li><strong>Essential:</strong> Needed for core site functionality (always on).</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Google Analytics for performance tracking.</li>
          <li><strong>Marketing:</strong> Meta Pixel for ad retargeting.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white leading-relaxed">
          You can manage cookies via our cookie banner. Blocking analytics or marketing cookies may limit some site features.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Disclosures</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-off-white">
          <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Google Workspace and hosting providers (UK/EU).</li>
          <li><strong>Professional advisers:</strong> Accountants and lawyers (UK-based).</li>
          <li><strong>Authorities:</strong> Where legally required.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white leading-relaxed">No international transfers outside UK/EEA.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Data Security</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-off-white">
          <li>SSL encryption on all pages.</li>
          <li>Access controls for employees and contractors.</li>
          <li>Regular security audits.</li>
          <li>Incident response within 24 hours for notifiable breaches.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Data Retention</h2>
        <div class="mt-5 overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full min-w-[460px] border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/20">
                <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 text-yellow">Data Type</th>
                <th class="text-left py-3 text-yellow">Retention Period</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-off-white">
              <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Enquiry data</td>
                <td class="py-3">3 years post-last contact</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Demo requests</td>
                <td class="py-3">12 months</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-white/10">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Analytics</td>
                <td class="py-3">26 months (Google Analytics)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold">Cookies</td>
                <td class="py-3">Session or up to 2 years</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Your Legal Rights</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-off-white">
          <li>Access: Request a copy of your data.</li>
          <li>Rectification: Correct inaccuracies.</li>
          <li>Erasure: Delete data ("right to be forgotten").</li>
          <li>Restriction: Pause processing.</li>
          <li>Portability: Receive data in machine-readable format.</li>
          <li>Object: Challenge legitimate interest processing.</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for marketing cookies.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white leading-relaxed">No automated decision-making is used.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">How To Exercise Rights</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white leading-relaxed">
          Email <a href="mailto:hello@humtech.ai" class="text-blue-light hover:text-yellow underline underline-offset-4">hello@humtech.ai</a> with your full name, company, the specific right requested, and supporting ID if identity verification is needed.
          We respond within 1 month (extendable to 3 months for complex requests). No fee is charged unless requests are excessive or repetitive.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Complaints</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white leading-relaxed">
          Contact us first at <a href="mailto:hello@humtech.ai" class="text-blue-light hover:text-yellow underline underline-offset-4">hello@humtech.ai</a>.
          You can also escalate to the ICO:
          <a href="https://www.ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-light hover:text-yellow underline underline-offset-4 ml-1">www.ico.org.uk</a>
          (Helpline: 0303 123 1113).
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Contact Details</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white leading-relaxed">
          HumTech<br />
          Chris Silver (Director)<br />
          Email:
          <a href="mailto:hello@humtech.ai" class="text-blue-light hover:text-yellow underline underline-offset-4 ml-1">hello@humtech.ai</a>
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow">Changes To This Policy</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-off-white leading-relaxed">
          We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be communicated to site visitors.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
